# TODO Files in Packages

**This rule overrides the user's global TODO.md rule for this workspace.**

For typesugar, track TODO items in `TODO.md` files within individual packages:

- `packages/type-system/TODO.md` — refined types, newtypes, HKT, Vec, etc.
- `packages/units/TODO.md` — dimensional analysis, unit conversions
- `packages/testing/TODO.md` — assertions, property-based testing, Arbitrary
- `packages/fp/TODO.md` — Option, Either, IO, typeclasses
- `packages/std/TODO.md` — extension methods, match, do-notation
- etc.

**Do NOT use:**

- `~/src/TODO.md` (global personal TODO)
- `~/src/typesugar/TODO.md` (repo-level TODO)

**Format:**

```markdown
# TODO

## Roadmap

- [ ] [date] Feature description — context/inspiration

## Bugs

- [ ] [date] Bug description
```

When adding items, include the date and source of inspiration (e.g., "inspired by Iron", "from Squants").
